snippet.title: Wuthering Waves · Dev Talk · Prelude EP. 1 - The Intro
snippet.description:
Dear Rovers,

Introducing "Wuthering Waves · Dev Talk · Prelude". 
A series where we give you an insight into Wuthering Waves' development and some glances behind the scenes.
Our first episode will include a General Introduction of Wuthering Waves, its Development Process, and our future Plans, to help our players learn and understand Wuthering Waves from various perspectives.

Heed the Prelude. 

Pre sign-up for the game:
https://wutheringwaves.kurogame.com/en

♦ Check out our other official links
Official Website: https://wutheringwaves.kurogame.com/en
Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Wuthering-Waves-108346541748778
Official Discord: https://discord.gg/wutheringwaves 
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/Wuthering_Waves
Official Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/WutheringWaves

#WutheringWaves
